String.hash



User inputs long url into view

User clicks button to convert

Within Controller perform url shortening convertion and store long and short url pair in database (long_url, short_url)

Open a new page with the short url link, link directs to the long url
			


url structure

		base_path to get to our server  +  the "unique" extension that describes the long url	








